TY  - JOUR
TI  - Robust Rank Tests of the Unit Root Hypothesis
AU  - Hasan, M. N.
AU  - Koenker, R. W.
AB  - [We consider a family of rank tests based on the regression rank score process introduced by Gutenbrunner and Jurečková (1992) to test the unit root hypothesis in economic time series. In contrast to tests based on least squares methods, the rank tests are asymptotically Gaussian under the null hypothesis, and have excellent power--particularly under innovation processes exhibiting heavy tails.]
